id: pm-nnaq
title: Expose schema.unknown_field_policy via pm config set schema-unknown-field-policy
description: "schema.unknown_field_policy (allow/warn/strict) controls how item I/O handles metadata keys not in the runtime field registry. It is defined in RuntimeSchemaSettings (src/types.ts:400), has defaults in constants.ts (allow), and is honored in item-format.ts, but it is not settable via pm config set. Projects that want to catch typos in field names (strict mode) or surface warnings (warn mode) must hand-edit settings.json."
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 3
tags[3]: "area:config","area:schema",customization
created_at: "2026-06-07T10:08:25.196Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-07T10:15:55.978Z"
author: audit-cli-schema-agent
acceptance_criteria: "- pm config set schema_unknown_field_policy allow|warn|strict updates the setting\n- pm config get schema_unknown_field_policy returns the current value\n- pm config list includes the key\n- CONFIGURATION.md documents this setting with use-case examples"
parent: pm-8jdc
risk: low
confidence: high
body: "## Context\n\nschema.unknown_field_policy is:\n- Defined: src/types.ts:400 (RuntimeUnknownFieldPolicy)\n- Validated: src/core/store/settings-validator.ts:285\n- Honored: src/core/item/item-format.ts:89 (unknownFieldPolicy: options.schema.unknown_field_policy)\n- Default: 'allow' (src/core/shared/constants.ts:290)\n- Listed in serializeSettings orderObject call (src/core/store/settings.ts:789)\n\nBut not in:\n- CONFIG_KEY_VALUES (src/cli/commands/config.ts:44-92)\n- NESTED_SETTING_DESCRIPTORS (src/core/config/nested-settings.ts)\n\nAdding it to NESTED_SETTING_DESCRIPTORS with kind='string' and choices=['allow','warn','strict'] follows the established pattern.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- pm config set schema_unknown_field_policy allow|warn|strict updates the setting\n- pm config get schema_unknown_field_policy returns the current value\n- pm config list includes the key\n- CONFIGURATION.md documents this setting with use-case examples\n\n## Evidence\n\n- src/types.ts:400 (RUNTIME_UNKNOWN_FIELD_POLICY_VALUES = ['allow','warn','strict'])\n- src/core/store/settings-validator.ts:285 (vLiteral validation)\n- src/core/config/nested-settings.ts:54-206 (NESTED_SETTING_DESCRIPTORS — missing this key)"
